---
title: Beef Steaks and Worcestershire Cream with Mushrooms and Garlic Green Beans
description: It's steak night and we've got another goodie for ya, full of protein and veg! The garlic green beans are a wonder and the Worcestershire cream will have you licking the plate clean!

